SIMPLE: eternally
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eternally
<hw>E*ter"nal*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an eternal
manner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That which is morally good or evil at any time or in any case,
must be also <qex>eternally</qex> and unchangeably so.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Where western gales <qex>eternally</qex> reside.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eterne</ent>⟦br⟧
